Monster Punch: In a large pitcher or punch bowl, combine and stir cranberry, apple and grape juice; refrigerate. When ready to serve, add cola, strawberries, and the floating hand if desired (directions below). Scary Punch: In a large pitcher or punch bowl, combine orange soda and club soda; stir. Drop in scoops of orange sherbet and whipped topping. Add marshmallows and place a drop of red food coloring on each marshmallow for a floating eyeball effect.